abstract: >
  QuantoniumOS is an educational cryptographic platform exploring 
  quantum-inspired algorithms and wave-based encryption techniques. 
  It provides implementations in Python, C++, and Rust with a focus 
  on cross-implementation validation and statistical verification
  of cryptographic properties.
